QuestData.Title: Kill Kher Shan
QuestData.Description: Kher Shan is one big dooker.$b$bGrooked all my sons! Ick Ick, Nab Nab, Eet Eet, Bitty Bitty, and the others I can't remember.$b$bWikket wanna help hozen? Go grook Kher Shan!$b$bThe dooker's over there.$b$b<Nibi Nibi points to the east.>
